  "description": "N3XT is a fully reserved, Wyoming-chartered special purpose depository institution offering instant USD B2B payments with programmable, real-time settlement and 24/7 liquidity. All deposits are backed 1:1 by cash or ultra-short-term U.S. Treasuries. N3XT also issues the N3XT Digital Dollar (NDD), a tokenized deposit on Ethereum (ERC-20) that represents a 1:1 claim on bank-held USD, enabling on-chain payments between KYC/KYB-verified counterparties.",
